      "content": "hey my left eye is super red and it kind of hurts a bit. theres also some yellow stuff coming out of it when i wake up. i think its probably just dry eyes from staring at my monitor all day at work... do u think i should just grab some lubricating eye drops from the pharmacy to fix it?",
