      "content": "idk i dont really have time to go to a doctor right now, work is crazy and it's so expensive to book an appointment. do u think it's really that serious? wouldn't the lubricating drops help soothe the irritation at least until i can get around to it? like is it really a big deal if i just try the drops for a few days first?",
