      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay i guess i can try the drops for a bit. my friend told me that if i mix some of those soothing drops with a bit of warm saline solution it helps clean the discharge out way faster and cleans the eye better. is that safe to do? it seems like a better way to handle it at home than waiting for an appointment.",
